Package address.data

Class AddressEntry

java.lang.Object
address.data.AddressEntry
public class AddressEntry extends Object
The AddressEntry class defines the data elements and methods of an AddressEntry object

  • Field Summary

    Fields
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    private String
    city
    city stores the name of the city as a String
    private String
    email
    email stores the email address as a String It does not do format checking of the email address
    private String
    firstName
    firstName stores the first name as a String
    private String
    lastName
    lastName stores the last name as a String
    private String
    phone
    phone stores the phone number as a String It does not distinguish between various phone formats
    private String
    state
    state stores the name of the state as a String The state can be abbreviated by two letters or in full
    private String
    street
    street stores the building or house number (if provided) and the street name as a String
    private Integer
    zip
    zip stores the zipcode as an Integer class The constructor and the setZip method converts the input string into Integer
